webcut volume 25 43 23 32 42 29  with plane from surface 279  

imprint all
merge all

#Mesh
#BL
create boundary_layer 1
modify boundary_layer 1 uniform height 0.02 growth 1.2 layers 3 
modify boundary_layer 1 add curve 17 surface 19 
modify boundary_layer 1 continuity on

#Inlet Curve
curve 17  interval 16
curve 17  scheme equal
curve 17  interval 16
curve 17  scheme equal
mesh curve 17 

curve 49  interval 16
